1
00:01:38,359 --> 00:01:40,159
Letting your men collude with the police

2
00:01:40,280 --> 00:01:40,760
Punish

3
00:01:42,680 --> 00:01:44,239
Insubordination and betrayal

4
00:01:44,560 --> 00:01:45,079
Punish

5
00:01:47,519 --> 00:01:48,640
Attempting a coup

6
00:01:49,040 --> 00:01:49,680
Punish

7
00:01:59,680 --> 00:02:01,159
I was deceived and wasn't thinking straight

8
00:02:02,879 --> 00:02:05,079
The Elders and Wei Hao kept instigating me

9
00:02:05,760 --> 00:02:06,799
To drive a wedge between us

10
00:02:07,519 --> 00:02:09,639
That's why I acted like such a jerk

11
00:02:11,960 --> 00:02:12,639
I deserve to die

12
00:02:14,280 --> 00:02:15,479
I deserve to die

13
00:02:16,879 --> 00:02:17,960
I accept my punishment

14
00:02:25,000 --> 00:02:25,639
Uncle Kun

15
00:02:26,080 --> 00:02:26,639
Uncle Kun

16
00:02:28,599 --> 00:02:29,280
Uncle Kun

17
00:02:30,479 --> 00:02:31,879
I understand everything now

18
00:02:32,479 --> 00:02:34,800
You are the only one who treats me best

19
00:02:37,240 --> 00:02:39,639
I've already killed that traitor Wei Hao with my own hands

20
00:02:41,439 --> 00:02:42,400
I beg you

21
00:02:44,000 --> 00:02:45,360
I'm begging you

22
00:02:45,719 --> 00:02:46,560
I beg you

23
00:02:50,360 --> 00:02:51,560
Give me one more

24
00:02:52,840 --> 00:02:53,919
I beg you to give me one more

25
00:02:54,000 --> 00:02:55,280
Chance to serve you

26
00:02:57,120 --> 00:02:58,159
I beg you

27
00:02:59,080 --> 00:02:59,879
Uncle Kun

28
00:03:00,360 --> 00:03:01,319
I beg you

29
00:03:01,800 --> 00:03:02,879
Please, I beg you

30
00:03:03,400 --> 00:03:04,520
Please, I beg you

31
00:03:04,639 --> 00:03:05,439
Enough

32
00:03:23,240 --> 00:03:24,240
Look at you

33
00:03:26,960 --> 00:03:28,080
Considering that

34
00:03:28,879 --> 00:03:31,759
You've done a lot for Cang Feng

35
00:03:33,479 --> 00:03:35,400
You don't have to go to the Kennel

36
00:03:36,319 --> 00:03:37,240
This matter

37
00:03:38,639 --> 00:03:39,879
Ends here

38
00:03:40,960 --> 00:03:43,159
Just work hard under Zhijie from now on

39
00:03:44,479 --> 00:03:45,840
And make amends

40
00:03:51,960 --> 00:03:52,919
Thank you, Uncle Kun

41
00:03:53,159 --> 00:03:54,000
Thank you, Uncle Kun

42
00:03:59,280 --> 00:04:00,159
Thank you, Brother Jie

43
00:04:01,400 --> 00:04:02,400
Thank you, Brother Jie

44
00:04:03,280 --> 00:04:04,240
Thank you, Brother Jie

45
00:04:06,240 --> 00:04:06,879
All right

46
00:04:08,479 --> 00:04:09,719
You may all leave now

47
00:04:10,000 --> 00:04:11,479
I have something to discuss with Zhijie

48
00:04:21,959 --> 00:04:22,399
Uncle Kun.

49
00:04:23,199 --> 00:04:24,120
What are you doing?

50
00:04:24,560 --> 00:04:25,160
Get up.

51
00:04:29,439 --> 00:04:29,959
Uncle Kun,

52
00:04:30,319 --> 00:04:31,920
I executed Wei Hao while you were away,

53
00:04:33,439 --> 00:04:34,600
and offended The Elders.

54
00:04:34,800 --> 00:04:35,560
It was my fault.

55
00:04:37,519 --> 00:04:38,639
I'm willing to step down to apologize,

56
00:04:39,279 --> 00:04:40,240
to calm The Elders down.

57
00:04:43,800 --> 00:04:45,720
Yesterday, because of the bad weather,

58
00:04:46,279 --> 00:04:48,279
and having no signal at sea...

59
00:04:49,519 --> 00:04:51,120
Wei Hao was always causing trouble.

60
00:04:51,279 --> 00:04:52,519
He should have been dealt with long ago.

61
00:04:53,040 --> 00:04:54,040
The Elders

62
00:04:55,000 --> 00:04:57,439
use their seniority to suppress you all.

63
00:04:58,120 --> 00:04:59,319
They even instigated Wei Hao

64
00:05:00,040 --> 00:05:01,959
to do dirty work for them.

65
00:05:02,639 --> 00:05:04,519
I've always turned a blind eye to it.

66
00:05:07,600 --> 00:05:09,160
It's good that you helped me today

67
00:05:09,319 --> 00:05:10,439
to teach them a lesson.

68
00:05:12,040 --> 00:05:13,360
Lately, people in the syndicate

69
00:05:13,360 --> 00:05:15,480
have been praising your capability.

70
00:05:16,360 --> 00:05:17,120
Given time,

71
00:05:18,279 --> 00:05:20,000
you'll definitely be able to help me run things.

72
00:05:20,600 --> 00:05:23,360
Why are you talking about stepping down?

73
00:05:24,680 --> 00:05:25,240
Uncle Kun,

74
00:05:27,519 --> 00:05:28,800
Cang Feng can't do without you.

75
00:05:30,600 --> 00:05:31,879
But it doesn't matter if I'm here or not.

76
00:05:33,680 --> 00:05:35,279
You saved my life.

77
00:05:37,079 --> 00:05:38,879
I've risked my life for you all these years.

78
00:05:40,160 --> 00:05:41,560
Reputation, status...

79
00:05:42,160 --> 00:05:42,879
I have them all now.

80
00:05:43,720 --> 00:05:45,360
Now that Cang Feng has mostly gone legit,

81
00:05:46,920 --> 00:05:47,680
I was thinking

82
00:05:48,560 --> 00:05:49,519
it's time for me to step down.

83
00:05:50,240 --> 00:05:51,279
I want to live a normal life.

84
00:05:54,120 --> 00:05:55,360
I want to take a break.

85
00:05:56,639 --> 00:05:58,240
You don't have to step down for that.

86
00:05:58,839 --> 00:06:01,360
The resort at Xingzhou Port is perfect for you.

87
00:06:02,279 --> 00:06:03,040
Thank you, Uncle Kun.

88
00:06:04,240 --> 00:06:04,920
But...

89
00:06:05,439 --> 00:06:06,439
the winery in the UK...

90
00:06:06,439 --> 00:06:07,439
I've already sorted everything out.

91
00:06:10,480 --> 00:06:11,319
The UK?

92
00:06:19,360 --> 00:06:20,360
The UK...

93
00:06:21,240 --> 00:06:22,720
The weather is too cold and damp.

94
00:06:23,959 --> 00:06:24,720
Have you forgotten?

95
00:06:26,360 --> 00:06:29,040
Pneumonia almost killed you when you were ten.

96
00:06:30,519 --> 00:06:31,319
But, Uncle Kun...

97
00:06:33,160 --> 00:06:33,680
I...

98
00:06:35,199 --> 00:06:35,959
Back then,

99
00:06:37,279 --> 00:06:39,120
you were scavenging for food in the trash.

100
00:06:41,160 --> 00:06:42,480
Out of so many orphans,

101
00:06:44,399 --> 00:06:45,720
I only took you with me.

102
00:06:47,160 --> 00:06:48,439
You want to leave now

103
00:06:55,399 --> 00:06:56,680
because of Hao Yu?

104
00:07:03,160 --> 00:07:04,199
And for myself.

105
00:07:08,519 --> 00:07:09,319
I remember

106
00:07:10,040 --> 00:07:11,519
when you were twelve,

107
00:07:12,519 --> 00:07:15,720
escorting rough jade with me in the Lashio jungle.

108
00:07:15,920 --> 00:07:17,199
You were shot three times,

109
00:07:18,079 --> 00:07:19,160
but didn't make a sound.

110
00:07:20,720 --> 00:07:22,800
At fifteen, you helped me snatch the Dragon Head Staff.

111
00:07:24,439 --> 00:07:25,800
Your intestines were spilling out,

112
00:07:26,600 --> 00:07:27,800
but you still held on.

113
00:07:30,639 --> 00:07:33,519
I've never worried that you would betray me.

114
00:07:35,519 --> 00:07:36,279
However,

115
00:07:38,920 --> 00:07:39,959
before you leave,

116
00:07:42,120 --> 00:07:44,879
Councilor Zhu has something for you to do.

117
00:07:45,519 --> 00:07:47,360
And only you can get it done.

118
00:07:48,680 --> 00:07:49,279
Of course,

119
00:07:51,040 --> 00:07:52,120
I don't want to either.

120
00:07:52,680 --> 00:07:53,600
But to be a councilor,

121
00:07:53,879 --> 00:07:55,199
to become an insider,

122
00:07:56,199 --> 00:07:57,920
I need that money.

123
00:07:59,399 --> 00:08:01,639
I believe you've heard about that new shipment.

124
00:08:01,879 --> 00:08:03,519
It's both a new and limited edition.

125
00:08:03,879 --> 00:08:06,600
So police from all countries are keeping a close eye on it.

126
00:08:08,439 --> 00:08:09,279
I know

127
00:08:10,680 --> 00:08:12,519
this deal is extremely dangerous.

128
00:08:14,000 --> 00:08:15,360
But the more dangerous it is,

129
00:08:17,560 --> 00:08:18,639
the more tempting it is.

130
00:08:20,120 --> 00:08:22,160
Everyone in the underworld is fighting for it.

131
00:08:23,839 --> 00:08:25,560
Whoever possesses it

132
00:08:26,399 --> 00:08:28,199
owns nearly half of Selong Port.

133
00:08:28,279 --> 00:08:28,879
I accept.

134
00:08:43,039 --> 00:08:43,799
Rest assured.

135
00:08:45,159 --> 00:08:46,639
As long as these old bones are here,

136
00:08:48,840 --> 00:08:50,720
I will be your best scabbard.

137
00:08:56,840 --> 00:08:58,840
And to think I thought he was a wolf.

138
00:08:59,320 --> 00:09:01,159
But now, for the sake of a wild cat...

139
00:09:01,639 --> 00:09:03,360
Ignoring his elders is one thing,

140
00:09:03,679 --> 00:09:06,279
but now he wants to betray Cang Feng, betray me.

141
00:09:07,360 --> 00:09:09,679
Ignoring the resort at Xingzhou Port,

142
00:09:10,000 --> 00:09:11,399
he wants to go to England of all places.

143
00:09:11,879 --> 00:09:12,919
This is clearly

144
00:09:14,360 --> 00:09:16,519
an attempt to leave my sphere of influence.

145
00:09:18,960 --> 00:09:19,919
It's a pity.

146
00:09:21,440 --> 00:09:23,240
A fine knife like Ji Zhijie.

147
00:09:24,000 --> 00:09:26,480
But having him wade through these muddy waters one last time

148
00:09:27,039 --> 00:09:28,600
is making the best use of him.

149
00:09:31,159 --> 00:09:32,559
If this knife is going to break,

150
00:09:35,279 --> 00:09:37,960
it must break inside this scabbard of mine.

151
00:09:46,480 --> 00:09:49,159
You've checked for six months and found nothing on that girl.

152
00:09:50,840 --> 00:09:52,639
Back then, it took you less than a month

153
00:09:52,840 --> 00:09:54,639
to get the undercover agent's file

154
00:09:54,639 --> 00:09:56,440
from Guan Renjie.

155
00:09:58,360 --> 00:09:59,720
What's wrong with you now?

156
00:10:08,960 --> 00:10:10,159
So many people are watching this shipment.

157
00:10:10,679 --> 00:10:12,159
This is like sending us to collect debts in Hell.

158
00:10:18,679 --> 00:10:19,960
I... I didn't mean that.

159
00:10:20,480 --> 00:10:21,200
I just felt...

160
00:10:27,559 --> 00:10:28,039
What's wrong?

161
00:10:31,039 --> 00:10:33,440
I saw you've been busy from day to night.

162
00:10:33,600 --> 00:10:34,399
I was afraid you were hungry.

163
00:10:37,440 --> 00:10:38,840
What have you guys been busy with these past two days?

164
00:10:39,720 --> 00:10:41,000
I haven't even seen you.

165
00:10:45,360 --> 00:10:46,799
It has been a bit busy lately.

166
00:10:47,200 --> 00:10:48,559
Once I'm done with this period,

167
00:10:48,559 --> 00:10:49,440
I'll spend some quality time with you.

168
00:10:49,600 --> 00:10:50,039
Okay?

169
00:10:51,399 --> 00:10:52,240
When that time comes,

170
00:10:52,720 --> 00:10:54,080
let's move to England, okay?

171
00:10:59,240 --> 00:11:00,440
What kind of joke is this now?

172
00:11:00,919 --> 00:11:02,159
I'm not joking.

173
00:11:03,639 --> 00:11:04,600
You can start

174
00:11:04,600 --> 00:11:06,080
packing the things you like soon.

175
00:11:06,080 --> 00:11:07,200
Go to England first and wait for me there.

176
00:11:09,559 --> 00:11:10,080
Is...

177
00:11:10,799 --> 00:11:12,240
Did something happen?

178
00:11:13,519 --> 00:11:15,600
If The Elders are giving you a hard time,

179
00:11:15,600 --> 00:11:16,639
I'll go apologize right now.

180
00:11:16,799 --> 00:11:18,000
I'm sorry, I shouldn't have...

181
00:11:18,360 --> 00:11:20,159
I shouldn't have offended Wei Hao and Jia...

182
00:11:20,759 --> 00:11:21,879
Who would dare give me a hard time?

183
00:11:22,039 --> 00:11:22,879
Except for what I want,

184
00:11:22,879 --> 00:11:23,799
and what I want to do myself.

185
00:11:29,480 --> 00:11:30,000
What's wrong?

186
00:11:31,000 --> 00:11:31,679
You don't want to go?

187
00:11:32,679 --> 00:11:34,120
Didn't you tell me before

188
00:11:34,120 --> 00:11:35,399
that you liked England the most?

189
00:11:35,960 --> 00:11:36,759
No...

190
00:11:37,440 --> 00:11:38,039
I...

191
00:11:38,559 --> 00:11:41,240
I just got the nightclub, didn't I?

192
00:11:41,600 --> 00:11:43,480
I wanted to have a career of my own.

193
00:11:43,720 --> 00:11:45,279
This is just too sudden.

194
00:11:46,120 --> 00:11:47,519
It's just a nightclub.

195
00:11:48,759 --> 00:11:50,159
You'll have much more in the future.

196
00:11:52,200 --> 00:11:53,000
Then...

197
00:11:53,919 --> 00:11:55,240
what about Uncle Kun?

198
00:11:55,759 --> 00:11:57,080
Will he let us go so easily?

199
00:12:00,480 --> 00:12:01,080
Don't worry.

200
00:12:01,799 --> 00:12:03,000
I've already talked it over with Uncle Kun.

201
00:12:06,200 --> 00:12:06,759
Okay.

202
00:12:07,360 --> 00:12:08,840
Then I'll go get ready.

203
00:12:09,360 --> 00:12:10,000
Yeah, go ahead.

204
00:12:11,879 --> 00:12:12,279
Hao Yu.

205
00:12:19,799 --> 00:12:21,320
If you see anything recently,

206
00:12:21,320 --> 00:12:22,600
or hear anything bad,

207
00:12:23,559 --> 00:12:24,360
don't believe any of it.

208
00:12:25,279 --> 00:12:26,240
Only believe me.

209
00:12:29,360 --> 00:12:30,159
You must believe me.

210
00:12:37,200 --> 00:12:38,120
I have to go take care of something.

211
00:12:38,240 --> 00:12:38,759
Okay.

212
00:12:42,399 --> 00:12:42,799
Hello?

213
00:12:44,600 --> 00:12:45,200
I've already asked Jia Li

214
00:12:45,200 --> 00:12:46,840
to swap the Jade Guanyin for that old friend

215
00:12:46,840 --> 00:12:47,919
with a gold-inlaid ivory one.

216
00:12:48,279 --> 00:12:48,799
Don't worry.

217
00:13:08,840 --> 00:13:10,399
If Ji Zhijie quits Cang Feng

218
00:13:10,879 --> 00:13:12,039
and moves straight to the UK,

219
00:13:12,480 --> 00:13:14,600
all my previous plans will be in vain.

220
00:13:14,679 --> 00:13:15,120
Don't worry.

221
00:13:16,320 --> 00:13:17,120
I've already found out

222
00:13:17,440 --> 00:13:18,240
who the buyer is.

223
00:13:18,399 --> 00:13:19,519
His name is Suchat Phamang.

224
00:13:20,919 --> 00:13:22,399
Based on the clues you provided,

225
00:13:23,240 --> 00:13:23,919
I found out that

226
00:13:24,399 --> 00:13:26,879
Ji Zhijie ordered a custom gift

227
00:13:28,000 --> 00:13:28,919
at the antique shop on Lotus Street.

228
00:13:30,919 --> 00:13:32,000
But there are so many antique shops.

229
00:13:32,080 --> 00:13:33,120
How did you guess which one?

230
00:13:35,559 --> 00:13:37,200
They've always been so secretive,

231
00:13:37,320 --> 00:13:38,840
I really couldn't find an opening.

232
00:13:39,559 --> 00:13:40,120
Luckily,

233
00:13:40,600 --> 00:13:42,960
I saw a gift box on Ji Zhijie's desk.

234
00:13:48,200 --> 00:13:49,320
Zhong Jiali had previously

235
00:13:49,720 --> 00:13:50,879
given one to Ji Zhijie too.

236
00:13:52,240 --> 00:13:53,600
I also heard Ji Zhijie mention

237
00:13:54,399 --> 00:13:56,679
it was an antique shop in Xingzhou Port.

238
00:13:58,360 --> 00:14:00,399
But who exactly is Suchat?

239
00:14:04,559 --> 00:14:05,600
Suchat Phamang.

240
00:14:06,240 --> 00:14:07,879
He is the biggest smuggler in Southeast Asia.

241
00:14:09,279 --> 00:14:11,399
If we can catch him trading with Ji Zhijie,

242
00:14:12,360 --> 00:14:14,000
we can not only bring Ji Zhijie to justice

243
00:14:14,679 --> 00:14:15,720
but also take down Cang Feng.

244
00:14:16,039 --> 00:14:18,000
But Cang Feng has been trying to go legit.

245
00:14:20,159 --> 00:14:21,960
Liang Zhaokun is also running for councilor.

246
00:14:22,960 --> 00:14:25,440
Ji Zhijie has been liquidating his Swiss accounts.

247
00:14:26,320 --> 00:14:27,440
Liang Zhaokun...

248
00:14:27,840 --> 00:14:29,360
he wants to go legit and become a councilor.

249
00:14:30,559 --> 00:14:32,879
He needs thirty million for bribes.

250
00:14:33,000 --> 00:14:34,000
Thirty million.

251
00:14:35,440 --> 00:14:36,679
They will definitely take the risk.

252
00:14:37,960 --> 00:14:38,960
Once they go legit,

253
00:14:40,000 --> 00:14:41,799
everything in Selong Port will change.

254
00:14:43,440 --> 00:14:44,440
I know all of this.

255
00:14:44,600 --> 00:14:46,039
But I just feel something isn't right.

256
00:14:51,799 --> 00:14:52,799
You just need to remember,

257
00:14:53,519 --> 00:14:54,279
the people of Cang Feng...

258
00:14:54,360 --> 00:14:55,080
all this time,

259
00:14:55,159 --> 00:14:57,159
they've committed murder, arson, and every crime.

260
00:14:57,519 --> 00:14:58,639
They can legitimize their business,

261
00:14:58,799 --> 00:14:59,840
but they can't cleanse their hearts.

262
00:15:02,200 --> 00:15:04,200
Do you remember how Superintendent Guan died?

263
00:15:05,639 --> 00:15:06,600
And your family...

264
00:15:07,440 --> 00:15:08,519
how they all met their end?

265
00:15:08,519 --> 00:15:09,159
Have you forgotten?

266
00:15:15,799 --> 00:15:16,440
I'm sorry.

267
00:15:19,919 --> 00:15:22,039
It's going to be hard on you for a while.

268
00:15:22,399 --> 00:15:24,200
Find out the time and location of the deal ASAP.

269
00:15:26,000 --> 00:15:27,600
As long as we work closely together,

270
00:15:29,000 --> 00:15:30,840
we can definitely take them all down.

271
00:15:31,919 --> 00:15:32,519
When that happens,

272
00:15:33,399 --> 00:15:34,879
you can be completely free of him.

273
00:15:37,120 --> 00:15:37,799
And we...

274
00:15:41,279 --> 00:15:43,399
can start over...

275
00:15:46,919 --> 00:15:48,399
Okay, I know all that.

276
00:15:48,639 --> 00:15:50,360
I'm worried more people will show up soon.

277
00:15:50,559 --> 00:15:51,240
I'm leaving now.

278
00:16:11,840 --> 00:16:13,759
As long as we find the time and location,

279
00:16:14,320 --> 00:16:14,840
this time,

280
00:16:15,080 --> 00:16:16,720
we will definitely wipe out Cang Feng.

281
00:16:21,000 --> 00:16:22,679
I still feel something is wrong.

282
00:16:35,759 --> 00:16:36,759
Hurry up and move these wooden crates inside.

283
00:16:36,960 --> 00:16:37,480
Close the door tight.

284
00:16:37,600 --> 00:16:38,480
Don't let Madam see them.

285
00:16:38,679 --> 00:16:40,120
Hurry and take these cardboard boxes away to be destroyed.

286
00:16:40,240 --> 00:16:40,919
Don't let Madam see.

287
00:16:44,759 --> 00:16:46,039
Don't let me see what?

288
00:16:50,399 --> 00:16:51,360
Old books, just old books.

289
00:16:59,320 --> 00:17:00,440
Ji Zhijie hates it the most...

290
00:17:00,559 --> 00:17:02,080
...when people get involved with Zhu Shuyi.

291
00:17:02,879 --> 00:17:03,799
Now suddenly acting like this...

292
00:17:04,279 --> 00:17:05,279
...there must be some secret.

293
00:17:11,559 --> 00:17:13,599
I was wondering why you're all so secretive every day...

294
00:17:13,720 --> 00:17:14,799
...holding meetings behind closed doors.

295
00:17:15,559 --> 00:17:17,079
Turns out you're helping your boss...

296
00:17:17,240 --> 00:17:18,359
...find a new Madam, aren't you?

297
00:17:18,440 --> 00:17:19,079
Is that it?

298
00:17:20,000 --> 00:17:20,880
Trashy tabloids.

299
00:17:21,079 --> 00:17:22,720
We're throwing them out because they write nonsense.

300
00:17:23,559 --> 00:17:24,680
Those things you just moved in...

301
00:17:24,680 --> 00:17:26,079
...those Nanyang rosewood crates...

302
00:17:26,759 --> 00:17:29,000
...are the Western antique instruments listed here, right?

303
00:17:29,319 --> 00:17:29,759
So...

304
00:17:30,440 --> 00:17:32,920
...is this a token of love from Ji Zhijie to her?

305
00:17:33,200 --> 00:17:34,160
Or is it a dowry?

306
00:17:34,880 --> 00:17:35,519
It's really not.

307
00:17:35,759 --> 00:17:36,880
You're really wronging Brother Jie.

308
00:17:37,640 --> 00:17:38,640
Then let me go in and see.

309
00:17:40,599 --> 00:17:42,359
Brother Jie ordered that no one can enter.

310
00:17:45,400 --> 00:17:46,119
Feihu.

311
00:17:46,720 --> 00:17:48,200
I usually treat you well, don't I?

312
00:17:49,359 --> 00:17:50,000
So what now?

313
00:17:50,440 --> 00:17:52,000
Your boss is going to marry a new Madam...

314
00:17:52,200 --> 00:17:54,519
...so now you're here to bully me, is that it?

315
00:17:54,720 --> 00:17:55,079
No...

316
00:17:55,519 --> 00:17:56,640
Madam, listen to me first.

317
00:17:57,039 --> 00:17:58,640
You can't get in without the password anyway.

318
00:17:58,799 --> 00:18:00,799
If you still consider me your Madam...

319
00:18:01,039 --> 00:18:02,599
...even if I have to chop this door down today...

320
00:18:02,759 --> 00:18:03,680
...I am going in.

321
00:18:04,039 --> 00:18:04,880
If Ji Zhijie asks...

322
00:18:04,960 --> 00:18:06,119
...just say it's my fault.

323
00:18:06,160 --> 00:18:07,240
It has nothing to do with you guys.

324
00:18:07,359 --> 00:18:08,039
Madam...

325
00:18:08,160 --> 00:18:09,200
Please don't make this hard for me.

326
00:18:09,920 --> 00:18:10,400
Fine.

327
00:18:11,160 --> 00:18:12,000
I won't make it hard for you.

328
00:18:13,200 --> 00:18:13,680
I'll do it myself.

329
00:18:13,759 --> 00:18:14,359
No, Madam...

330
00:18:14,759 --> 00:18:15,400
Let her look.

331
00:18:24,400 --> 00:18:24,920
You can go.

332
00:18:43,160 --> 00:18:44,480
Who upset our Mrs. Ji?

333
00:18:47,480 --> 00:18:49,839
No wonder you're in such a rush to send me to the UK.

334
00:18:50,559 --> 00:18:51,759
You just want to get me out of the way...

335
00:18:51,960 --> 00:18:53,240
...afraid I'll ruin your good time.

336
00:18:54,119 --> 00:18:56,519
I don't care if you have other ideas.

337
00:18:56,839 --> 00:18:57,559
But...

338
00:18:58,480 --> 00:19:00,319
...even if I'm being kicked out...

339
00:19:00,839 --> 00:19:02,759
...I want to catch you red-handed...

340
00:19:03,039 --> 00:19:04,119
...for my own peace of mind.

341
00:19:06,400 --> 00:19:07,000
How about this.

342
00:19:08,240 --> 00:19:09,880
Let's play a game together.

343
00:19:11,920 --> 00:19:13,160
If you guess the password correctly...

344
00:19:14,000 --> 00:19:14,880
...I'll let you in.

345
00:19:26,759 --> 00:19:27,680
What game?

346
00:19:27,680 --> 00:19:28,720
I'm not a mind reader.

347
00:19:29,160 --> 00:19:29,559
I...

348
00:20:53,000 --> 00:20:54,279
Isn't this what I...

349
00:21:00,720 --> 00:21:01,960
Didn't you tell me?

350
00:21:02,359 --> 00:21:04,640
Since you were little, you wanted a piano like this.

351
00:21:05,559 --> 00:21:06,599
Once you learned how to play...

352
00:21:06,599 --> 00:21:08,559
...you'd go play with the kids at the orphanage.

353
00:21:08,960 --> 00:21:10,240
So when I saw it, I bought it.

354
00:21:15,839 --> 00:21:16,279
Try it.

355
00:21:43,319 --> 00:21:45,000
I wanted to give you a surprise.

356
00:21:45,200 --> 00:21:46,000
But it's a bit difficult.

357
00:21:47,000 --> 00:21:47,960
There's no time like the present.

358
00:21:49,359 --> 00:21:50,000
Do you like it?

359
00:22:29,279 --> 00:22:31,039
Who knows if you've said these same words

360
00:22:31,640 --> 00:22:33,599
to Ms. Zhu as well?

361
00:22:37,480 --> 00:22:39,720
Since it's being donated to the orphanage in my name,

362
00:22:40,200 --> 00:22:41,240
then take me there.

363
00:22:44,799 --> 00:22:47,640
Don't tell me you don't plan to take me,

364
00:22:48,160 --> 00:22:49,359
but take Ms. Zhu instead?

365
00:22:51,519 --> 00:22:53,119
Of course I want to take you with me.

366
00:22:55,319 --> 00:22:56,160
But on that day,

367
00:22:56,160 --> 00:22:58,160
I've already bought the tickets to the UK.

368
00:22:59,160 --> 00:22:59,720
Besides,

369
00:23:00,039 --> 00:23:00,839
right now, with Councilor Zhu,

370
00:23:00,960 --> 00:23:02,400
we still have some business dealings.

371
00:23:03,200 --> 00:23:04,240
The details involved in this,

372
00:23:04,559 --> 00:23:06,079
I'll explain to you properly later.

373
00:23:06,480 --> 00:23:07,039
Okay?

374
00:23:16,160 --> 00:23:17,480
All in all,

375
00:23:18,160 --> 00:23:20,039
you actually just want to send me away.

376
00:23:22,440 --> 00:23:23,759
And you won't tell me anything,

377
00:23:26,000 --> 00:23:27,319
just taking me for a fool.

378
00:23:29,480 --> 00:23:30,240
I told you,

379
00:23:31,440 --> 00:23:33,319
no matter what happens, you must trust me.

380
00:23:34,079 --> 00:23:34,720
Trust me.

381
00:23:38,079 --> 00:23:38,799
However,

382
00:23:39,880 --> 00:23:41,640
why are you so jealous lately?

383
00:23:43,640 --> 00:23:44,559
What do you think?

384
00:24:04,039 --> 00:24:04,519
Boss.

385
00:24:19,079 --> 00:24:19,680
What is it?

386
00:24:21,160 --> 00:24:23,599
The surveillance and anti-bugging devices are installed.

387
00:24:23,839 --> 00:24:25,440
Waiting for you to go check and test them.

388
00:24:39,519 --> 00:24:40,279
I'll get to work now.

389
00:24:48,599 --> 00:24:49,720
As long as the power isn't cut,

390
00:24:49,839 --> 00:24:50,720
they will run normally.

391
00:24:51,200 --> 00:24:51,960
If the power gets cut,

392
00:24:52,240 --> 00:24:53,799
just turn on the backup power in advance.

393
00:25:12,799 --> 00:25:14,880
Tropical monsoon Siren is approaching the port.

394
00:25:14,880 --> 00:25:17,480
The Observatory announced the raising of Signal No. 10 earlier.

395
00:25:17,680 --> 00:25:19,200
Rainfall in all districts continues to increase.

396
00:25:19,759 --> 00:25:21,000
Violent winds and thunderstorms are forecast.

397
00:25:21,200 --> 00:25:23,160
Siren is gradually moving towards the northwest landmass.

398
00:25:23,160 --> 00:25:24,400
Winds are strengthening significantly.

399
00:25:24,400 --> 00:25:25,920
All piers need to temporarily suspend

400
00:25:25,920 --> 00:25:26,880
all maritime activities.

401
00:25:27,359 --> 00:25:29,319
Mountain roads are also prone to accidents.

402
00:25:29,319 --> 00:25:31,480
Citizens are advised to plan travel carefully.

403
00:25:31,599 --> 00:25:33,119
Stay indoors as much as possible.

404
00:25:33,279 --> 00:25:34,720
Secure windows and doors, beware of power outages,

405
00:25:34,720 --> 00:25:36,559
and accidents like landslides.

406
00:26:06,440 --> 00:26:07,119
Superintendent Li,

407
00:26:07,680 --> 00:26:09,440
Ji Zhijie's logistics factory on the outlying island...

408
00:26:10,039 --> 00:26:10,720
Is it...

409
00:26:10,759 --> 00:26:11,319
Three.

410
00:26:12,440 --> 00:26:12,960
Two.

411
00:26:14,160 --> 00:26:14,680
One.

412
00:26:15,400 --> 00:26:16,559
Feilong, ready the speedboat.

413
00:26:17,039 --> 00:26:17,519
Within thirty minutes,

414
00:26:17,519 --> 00:26:18,920
I want to see all container numbers repainted.

415
00:26:20,000 --> 00:26:20,559
Okay, Brother Jie.

416
00:26:28,119 --> 00:26:29,680
You can't go out in a typhoon.

417
00:26:30,920 --> 00:26:32,160
Rushing to see Ms. Zhu?

418
00:26:33,799 --> 00:26:35,079
Do you need me to prepare an umbrella for you?

419
00:27:10,119 --> 00:27:12,160
There's a problem at the logistics factory on the outlying island.

420
00:27:12,359 --> 00:27:13,160
I have to go over there.

421
00:27:14,839 --> 00:27:17,240
The police don't investigate affairs, do they?

422
00:27:20,119 --> 00:27:21,240
You stay home and be good.

423
00:27:21,839 --> 00:27:23,440
I'll have Chen Ma and Feihu stay with you.

424
00:27:25,079 --> 00:27:25,680
No need.

425
00:27:27,200 --> 00:27:28,559
I have nothing to do at home anyway.

426
00:27:29,279 --> 00:27:30,519
Chen Ma and the others are enough.

427
00:27:32,039 --> 00:27:32,960
Let Feihu go with you.

428
00:27:35,799 --> 00:27:36,680
Wait for me at home like a good girl.

429
00:28:10,119 --> 00:28:11,079
Chen Ma, Ah Ling.

430
00:28:11,480 --> 00:28:12,319
Miss, Miss.

431
00:28:13,599 --> 00:28:14,519
I heard

432
00:28:15,160 --> 00:28:17,119
this typhoon is really quite severe.

433
00:28:17,400 --> 00:28:18,119
Yes.

434
00:28:18,720 --> 00:28:19,759
You've been busy taking care of me,

435
00:28:19,960 --> 00:28:20,960
and haven't had time yet

436
00:28:20,960 --> 00:28:22,279
to seal windows and stock up for your homes?

437
00:28:22,960 --> 00:28:23,640
Yes.

438
00:28:24,599 --> 00:28:25,279
Chen Ma,

439
00:28:25,799 --> 00:28:26,799
don't you have a

440
00:28:26,799 --> 00:28:28,440
paralyzed mother-in-law in her nineties at home?

441
00:28:29,599 --> 00:28:30,519
And you, Ah Ling,

442
00:28:30,799 --> 00:28:32,000
your child is so young,

443
00:28:32,240 --> 00:28:33,160
and you live so far away.

444
00:28:33,400 --> 00:28:35,000
What if something happens to your house?

445
00:28:37,119 --> 00:28:37,839
How about this,

446
00:28:38,279 --> 00:28:39,079
tonight,

447
00:28:39,400 --> 00:28:40,720
you two go back first.

448
00:28:42,519 --> 00:28:43,480
Thank you, Miss.

449
00:28:43,759 --> 00:28:44,720
Thank you, Miss.

450
00:28:44,839 --> 00:28:46,279
You're welcome. Go quickly.

451
00:28:46,559 --> 00:28:47,599
Then we'll leave first.

452
00:28:48,240 --> 00:28:49,000
Then I'll leave first.
